/>咁你又要係果邊玩 唔可以就住黎洗錢 <br />\n第二實際啲嘅就係講英文果啲 最好去之前努力下 去到學日常同人交流多啲返黎必成大器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三考埋車先去<br />\n第四都係當去旅行下嘅心態 見識下世界有幾大 比自己一個機會放鬆下<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇去過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解你會知道今日會好天架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真有心想學好英文 我有個外國番黎既frd 話想學好英文 好撚易姐 嗱 我依家日撚日同你講英文 之後我個幾日真係有同佢係咁英文溝通 通常第一句就 Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你老母 之後都係一埋廣東廢話"},{"pid":"63ddb9f4f24c5e3a1c930d80df258a9becd2b6fe","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過去義遊 去做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n短線有台灣日本東南亞 通常係兩個禮拜到一個月<br />\n而家出黎做野先留意到有d咁既野 可惜冇假去咁耐<br />\n如果當時後生去耐d就好 幫到人又幫到自己<br />\n香港生活太物質主義 去回歸大自然過番簡樸生活仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去做義工係咪自已出錢？<br />\n去山區義教啲細路？<br />\n認真講句 唔係唔想<br />\n但呢啲野反而好似老啲會適合啲<br />\n我依家呢知年紀 有邊個真係會諗到咁偉大<br />\n有時都係比個社會逼到咁勢利"},{"pid":"a097d1f491057cf2ab8430709b8d7a336865aa71","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"仲有無 仲有無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ada68de003dd34e0aef74e49a858bc08a80396","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90b6611eab6b79406213e78924a4c3e592ea5d2","tid":183312,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T04:44:47.000Z","msg":"身邊個個去wh既人都無一個會話揾到大錢番黎"},{"pid":"5b4d2cb630eec5ba05525c19da0fb64fb73919e0","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身邊個個去wh既人都無一個會話揾到大錢番黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係淨係想搵到錢既  我知外國都唔會好得幾多 賺得黎但個邊物價貴我明既 所但好似睇落最難得搵到既係經驗囉 好似...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412e351e245ac1a545cc522375bf16eaefc37812","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"唔通真係要學山雞咁過台灣一轉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ebbdcee7a0c5a8cffa8659ae1bfbc9aa81d69f","tid":183312,"uid":71219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"想去就去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90928c40d22ef97d1a5ea189514902185fc4300e","tid":183312,"uid":5902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:25:36.000Z","msg":"留名睇分享"},{"pid":"bd8ee51d15fc8da88418cd9519045908cd3de8d0","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"留名留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14450d9fee5022b80e9c7eb0894b93ecaa0fb876","tid":183312,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:31:39.000Z","msg":"Anyone?"},{"pid":"4de36db3fafe571f2b10d7d0736d3ab124348e84","tid":183312,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>身邊個個去wh既人都無一個會話揾到大錢番黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係淨係想搵到錢既  我知外國都唔會好得幾多 賺得黎但個邊物價貴我明既 所但好似睇落最難得搵到既